          <a href="/itineraries"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-gold/40 hover:border-gold text-gold hover:bg-gold/5 font-sans text-xs tracking-ultra uppercase px-7 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300">
            Explore More Itineraries →
